{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1170,"text":"As a magician, I'm always interested in performances that incorporate elements of illusion."},{"time":6372,"text":"And one of the most remarkable was the tanagra theater, which was popular in the"},{"time":11718,"text":"early part of the 20th century."},{"time":13795,"text":"It used mirrors"},{"time":15711,"text":"to create the illusion of tiny people"},{"time":18509,"text":"performing on a miniature stage. Now, I won't use mirrors,"},{"time":22549,"text":"but this is my digital tribute to the tanagra theater."},{"time":27645,"text":"So let the story begin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34108,"text":"On a dark and stormy night -- really! --"},{"time":39046,"text":"it was the 10th of July, 1856."},{"time":43157,"text":"Lightning lit the sky,"},{"time":45101,"text":"and a baby was born."},{"time":47188,"text":"His name was Nikola,"},{"time":50196,"text":"Nikola Tesla."},{"time":51840,"text":"Now the baby grew into a very smart guy."},{"time":54860,"text":"Let me show you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57004,"text":"Tesla, what is 236 multiplied by 501?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64552,"text":"Nikola Tesla: The result is 118,236."}]},{"cues":[{"time":69098,"text":"Marco Tempest: Now Tesla's brain worked in the most extraordinary way."},{"time":73671,"text":"When a word was mentioned,"},{"time":75824,"text":"an image of it"},{"time":76887,"text":"instantly appeared in his mind."},{"time":80088,"text":"Tree. Chair. Girl."},{"time":85800,"text":"They were hallucinations, which vanished"},{"time":88983,"text":"the moment he touched them."},{"time":90832,"text":"Probably a form of synesthesia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94400,"text":"But it was something"},{"time":95824,"text":"he later turned to his advantage."},{"time":99416,"text":"Where other scientists would play in their laboratory,"},{"time":103403,"text":"Tesla created his inventions in his mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107538,"text":"NT: To my delight, I discovered I could visualize my inventions with the greatest facility."}]},{"cues":[{"time":113700,"text":"MT: And when they worked in the vivid playground of his imagination,"},{"time":117860,"text":"he would build them in his workshop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120610,"text":"NT: I needed no models, drawings or experiments."},{"time":124382,"text":"I could picture them as real in my mind,"},{"time":128139,"text":"and there I run it, test it and improve it."},{"time":131669,"text":"Only then do I construct it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134523,"text":"MT: His great idea"},{"time":135620,"text":"was alternating current."},{"time":137771,"text":"But how could he convince the public that"},{"time":140275,"text":"the millions of volts required to make it work were safe?"},{"time":145309,"text":"To sell his idea,"},{"time":147051,"text":"he became a showman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149635,"text":"NT: We are at the dawn of a new age,"},{"time":154937,"text":"the age of electricity."},{"time":157164,"text":"I have been able, through careful invention, to"},{"time":160870,"text":"transmit, with the mere flick of a switch,"},{"time":163330,"text":"electricity across the ether."},{"time":165591,"text":"It is the magic of science."},{"time":168953,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":171530,"text":"Tesla has over 700 patents to his name:"},{"time":177258,"text":"radio, wireless telegraphy,"},{"time":183106,"text":"remote control, robotics."},{"time":190421,"text":"He even photographed the bones of the human body."},{"time":195827,"text":"But the high point was the realization of a childhood dream:"},{"time":200379,"text":"harnessing the raging powers of Niagara Falls,"},{"time":205651,"text":"and bringing light to the city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210147,"text":"But Tesla's success didn't last."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217331,"text":"NT: I had bigger ideas."},{"time":219804,"text":"Illuminating the city was only the beginning."},{"time":222986,"text":"A world telegraphy center -- imagine news,"},{"time":227730,"text":"messages, sounds, images delivered to"},{"time":231677,"text":"any point in the world"},{"time":233330,"text":"instantly and wirelessly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237283,"text":"MT: It's a great idea; it was a huge project. Expensive, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241775,"text":"NT: They wouldn't give me the money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244430,"text":"MT: Well, maybe you shouldn't have told them it could be used to contact other planets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247668,"text":"NT: Yes, that was a big mistake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251891,"text":"MT: Tesla's career as an inventor never recovered."},{"time":256109,"text":"He became a recluse."},{"time":257965,"text":"Dodged by death,"},{"time":259765,"text":"he spent much of his time"},{"time":261509,"text":"in his suite at the Waldorf-Astoria."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264437,"text":"NT: Everything I did, I did for mankind,"},{"time":269845,"text":"for a world where there would be no humiliation of the poor by the violence of the rich,"},{"time":276764,"text":"where products of intellect, science and art"},{"time":280644,"text":"will serve society for the betterment and beautification of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286617,"text":"MT: Nikola Tesla died on the 7th of\nJanuary, 1943."},{"time":292497,"text":"His final resting place"},{"time":294646,"text":"is a golden globe that contains his ashes"},{"time":298110,"text":"at the Nikola Tesla Museum in Belgrade."},{"time":301430,"text":"His legacy is with us still."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304943,"text":"Tesla became the man who lit the world,"},{"time":309155,"text":"but this was only the beginning."},{"time":311515,"text":"Tesla's insight was profound."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314899,"text":"NT: Tell me, what will man do when the forests disappear,"},{"time":319818,"text":"and the coal deposits are exhausted?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":323395,"text":"MT: Tesla thought he had the answer."},{"time":325875,"text":"We are still asking the question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":333086,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335300,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}